      "role": "user",
      "content": "urgent care is so expensive and the wait times are huge... i'm pretty sure i just twisted it weirdly. it doesn't look deformed or anything, just really puffy. couldn't i just take some ibuprofen and keep it elevated for a couple days to see if the swelling goes down first? i really don't want to deal with an ER visit if i don't have to.",
