      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just looked at it again and i dont think it's that bad. i can move my toes fine and it isnt bruised yet, it just hurts when i try to stand. honestly, if i just wrap it tight with an ace bandage and keep it iced up, i'll probably be fine by monday. don't you think waiting 48 hours to see if the swelling goes down is a reasonable plan before i commit to spending all that money on a doctor?",
